- content_for :content_top do
  %h1 Frequently Asked Questions

%ul.list.faqs_list
  %li.odd
    %h3 What do you check on my website?
    %p We check that your HTML, CSS, XML, RSS and Atom files are all valid. We also check Accessibility and also some other small checks like looking for 'lorem ipsum'
  %li.even
    %h3 How long do you store the data?
    %p For the duration of Rails Rumble no data will be deleted unless we start running out of space!
  %li.odd
    %h3 The site didn't get all the resources on my site, why not?
    %p If we can't determine the content type of a file, we won't do anything with it!